### oRPC utils (`durable-execution-orpc-utils`)

Server-side APIs in [src/server.ts](mdc:durable-execution-orpc-utils/src/server.ts):

- `createTasksRouter(os, executor)` – exposes `enqueueTask` and `getTaskExecution`
- `convertClientProcedureToTask(executor, taskOptions, procedure, [clientOptions])` – wrap client oRPC procedure as a durable task

Client helpers in [src/client.ts](mdc:durable-execution-orpc-utils/src/client.ts):

- `createTaskClientHandles(client, tasks, [clientOptions])` – build typed handles with `enqueue()` and `getExecution()`
- `TasksRouterClient` – typed client for the server procedures

See usage in [README.md](mdc:durable-execution-orpc-utils/README.md)
